prompts.frontCover: Minimalist 2D vector art for a greeting card front. A serene beach scene at sunset. Two cartoon-style figures, a man and a woman, are sitting cross-legged on a simple, light-colored picnic blanket, facing each other with loving smiles. They are clinking together unique boba tea drinks served in stylized coconut shells, complete with large boba straws. The sunset is depicted with simple, elegant shapes and a warm, soft color palette: gentle waves of pastel pink, soft orange, and pale yellow fill the sky above a calm, deep blue ocean line. The overall composition is clean and uncluttered, focusing on the sweet interaction between the couple. Centered in the middle of the design, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Anniversary, my love". The art style is flat, with no gradients, emphasizing clean lines and charming simplicity.
